data.description:
NEED A HOME WITH 2 LIVING SPACES OR MOTHER IN LAW SUITE? The main house can be ALL MAIN LEVEL LIVING with the primary bedroom on the main featuring a full bathroom and large closet. The laundry is only a few steps up and easy to access! The kitchen features a large eat in space with a full walk in pantry, bright beautiful windows, and French doors that cascade out onto a paved & covered patio for entertaining. Large bonus room on the main level that could possibly be used as a second main floor bedroom!

The property also offers 2 additional sheds, 1 car single garage, 1 car single garage with a full apartment inside including a kitchenette and full bathroom!  Encompassed by a fully fenced yard, this home offers a private place to call your own! Listed by Melissa Dascoulias
